title: VA Indie Easy Pop Sept 2013 - Building Bridges (Dutch Treat I2 H
description:
Already the fifth Indie playlist from September 2013. Good Songs, Sound Good! What do you think?

All this, thanks to my imaginary "Best Indie" friend from PB. It's always nice to meet an idiot like myself. Some recognition maybe. Anyway we listened to about a thousand songs. Most were beautiful, some clearly good and some were just to good to keep quiet. So I put these songs in my September lists (although most of them are a bit older but you might have missed them too). But whatever reason; in my ears, the list has become quite special. The songs really support each other. All in HQ..... Enjoy,
